### Articles API Tests
### Following RFC 2616 HTTP/1.1 Protocol
### VS Code REST Client Extension Required

@baseUrl = {{baseUrl}}
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

###
# Get list of articles (Public access)
# GET /api/v1/articles
# Default pagination: page=1, per_page=20
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/articles HTTP/1.1

###
# Get articles with pagination
# GET /api/v1/articles?page=1&per_page=10
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/articles?page=1&per_page=10 HTTP/1.1

###
# Get articles filtered by source
# GET /api/v1/articles?source_id=1
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/articles?source_id=1 HTTP/1.1

###
# Get articles with date range filter
# GET /api/v1/articles?date_from=2024-01-01&date_to=2024-12-31
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/articles?date_from=2024-01-01&date_to=2024-12-31 HTTP/1.1

###
# Get articles with multiple filters
# GET /api/v1/articles?source_id=1&page=1&per_page=10&date_from=2024-01-01
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/articles?source_id=1&page=1&per_page=10&date_from=2024-01-01 HTTP/1.1

###
# Get article by ID (Public access)
# GET /api/v1/articles/{article_id}
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/articles/1 HTTP/1.1

###
# Get specific article details
# GET /api/v1/articles/{article_id}
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/articles/123 HTTP/1.1

###
# Delete article (Admin only)
# DELETE /api/v1/articles/{article_id}
# Requires admin authentication
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/articles/123 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
